codeGet:
select TWTVROLE_CODE code,  TWTVROLE_DESC description 
from twtvrole
where
 (:virtual_domain_id is null or
   TWTVROLE_CODE not in 
  (select role_name from virtual_domain_role where virtual_domain_id=:virtual_domain_id)
)
union
select 'GUEST', '*Guest (no authentication)' from dual 
where :virtual_domain_id is null or
   'GUEST' not in 
  (select role_name from virtual_domain_role where virtual_domain_id=:virtual_domain_id)
union
select 'ALLROLES', '*Authenticated Self Service user (with PIDM)' from dual
where :virtual_domain_id is null or
   'ALLROLES' not in 
  (select role_name from virtual_domain_role where virtual_domain_id=:virtual_domain_id)
union
select '-', '*Authenticated user without PIDM' from dual
where :virtual_domain_id is null or
   '-' not in 
  (select role_name from virtual_domain_role where virtual_domain_id=:virtual_domain_id)
order by 2
